br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/235205_fab747197b1c78ecca3081972737f808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F235205_fab747197b1c78ecca3081972737f808.jpg&h=56c6e803&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你體脂係3.6kg 唔係3.6%喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼訓睇過龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該大約6.2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0463c71e712c98f1b682cc20ecfda761b4670d40","tid":259863,"uid":28628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>160 43KG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人夠我癲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌由細到大(23歲)都食唔肥,小學瘦到要見營養師,BMI嚴重偏底,依家仲係UNDERWEIGHT RANGE<br />\n注定一世無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢度係極瘦撚 <br />\n160 43kg  你係輕度肥胖"},{"pid":"2e804f33130b52e43332f175432f5484a06b98ee","tid":259863,"uid":50926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:39:35.000Z","msg":"要增磅既話<br />\nWeight train + nutrition + 休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 計左你一日既maintenance calorie先<br />\n(Google macro calculator 大把）<br />\n2. 增磅既就加350-500 kcal<br />\n3. 1 g carbs= 4 kcal, 1 protein = 4 kcal, <br />\n1 g fat = 9 kcal<br />\n4. 50% calorie from carbs, 30 % from protein, 20% from fat<br />\n<br />\nE.g. 一個60 kg 既人<br />\n60 kg = 132 lbs, 1 lbs body mass requires 1 G protein for growth<br />\n一日攝取既protein = 132 g<br />\n(100 g skinless chicken breast: 30 protein)<br />\n<br />\nCarbs he needs = 132 x 5/3 = 220 g<br />\n(100 g rice: 28 g carbs, 100 g spaghetti = 72 g carbs...)<br />\n<br />\nFats he needs= 132 x 2/3 = 88 g<br />\n( from salmons, from olive oil...)<br />\n<br />\nDaily calorie he needs for add mass<br />\n= 132 x 4 + 220 x 4 + 88 x 9 + 500 = 2660 kcal<br />\n<br />\n不過前提係佢有合適既重量訓練先會長肉"},{"pid":"09ae68e7ac6c70d6b217c5a3139b53d0172faec7","tid":259863,"uid":50926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要增磅既話<br />\nWeight train + nutrition + 休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 計左你一日既maintenance calorie先<br />\n(Google macro calculator 大把）<br />\n2. 增磅既就加350-500 kcal<br />\n3. 1 g carbs= 4 kcal, 1 protein = 4 kcal, <br />\n1 g fat = 9 kcal<br />\n4. 50% calorie from carbs, 30 % from protein, 20% from fat<br />\n<br />\nE.g. 一個60 kg 既人<br />\n60 kg = 132 lbs, 1 lbs body mass requires 1 G protein for growth<br />\n一日攝取既protein = 132 g<br />\n(100 g skinless chicken breast: 30 protein)<br />\n<br />\nCarbs he needs = (132 / 0.3 ) x 0.5 / 4 = 220 g<br />\n(100 g rice: 28 g carbs, 100 g spaghetti = 72 g carbs...)<br />\n<br />\nFats he needs= 132 x 2/3 = 88 g<br />\n( from salmons, from olive oil...)<br />\n<br />\nDaily calorie he needs for add mass<br />\n= 132 x 4 + 220 x 4 + 88 x 9 + 500 = 2660 kcal<br />\n<br />\n不過前提係佢有合適既重量訓練先會長肉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5781abb70e0c0d4ac10e83f8b0590e6da68798c3","tid":259863,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"175 49kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd75eb45a901c4a85d8af69713676f52012570b","tid":259863,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>173<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 60kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想增到65kg</blockquote><br />\n174 58kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167ebe2a7af7998d04d14aeaef4c5070fae788e6","tid":259863,"uid":59936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"屌曬你地全部老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527f2134db280598d72072fb8ec4ce8935a349c2","tid":259863,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌曬你地全部老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閘住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dccf00be8a53fdc784ba7d7fd35e1f71befeb77","tid":259863,"uid":9788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要增磅既話<br />\nWeight train + nutrition + 休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 計左你一日既maintenance calorie先<br />\n(Google macro calculator 大把）<br />\n2. 增磅既就加350-500 kcal<br />\n3. 1 g carbs= 4 kcal, 1 protein = 4 kcal, <br />\n1 g fat = 9 kcal<br />\n4. 50% calorie from carbs, 30 % from protein, 20% from fat<br />\n<br />\nE.g. 一個60 kg 既人<br />\n60 kg = 132 lbs, 1 lbs body mass requires 1 G protein for growth<br />\n一日攝取既protein = 132 g<br />\n(100 g skinless chicken breast: 30 protein)<br />\n<br />\nCarbs he needs = (132 / 0.3 ) x 0.5 / 4 = 220 g<br />\n(100 g rice: 28 g carbs, 100 g spaghetti = 72 g carbs...)<br />\n<br />\nFats he needs= 132 x 2/3 = 88 g<br />\n( from salmons, from olive oil...)<br />\n<br />\nDaily calorie he needs for add mass<br />\n= 132 x 4 + 220 x 4 + 88 x 9 + 500 = 2660 kcal<br />\n<br />\n不過前提係佢有合適既重量訓練先會長肉</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n搵日研究下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbbb9592188f49dcbb2a1a3ac9be7a5c315278b","tid":259863,"uid":9788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>175 49kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n175 47-48kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b316de2250ea747d2aba4dbed384ed5d2bd5598","tid":259863,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/210640_a54fddcd1b2dfd4910fe9ae69d9f257f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F210640_a54fddcd1b2dfd4910fe9ae69d9f257f.jpg&h=541fb110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇巴打有舊骨凸出來<br />\n成日覺得好核突。。</blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲凸過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}